                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6347" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1618</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8630 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">身材变轻，大象也可起舞：Z银行轻型银行战略转型之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Light figure, the elephant can also dance: Z bank light bank strategic transformation road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曹翠珍，赵晓铃，马玉洁，何文菁，王俊婷，王琳曼</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Z银行</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">轻型银行；数字转型；大财富战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">light bank ;digital transformation; big wealth strategy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在我国“十四五”政策环境与互联网背景下,银行业更加注重高质量发展，以数字化为载体的轻资产运营模式成为银行的战略首选。早在2004年，Z银行便顺势主动求变，率先走上“轻型银行”改革之路，致力于转型发展成为我国最佳的商业银行，坚持轻型银行的战略目标，以零售业务为核心，实现了由1.0模式向2.0模式的转变；随着时代不断发展,金融科技的持续深化引起服务渠道及载体的数字化迁移、客户交易行为数字化、同业以及跨界竞争加剧等变化。面对环境变化，Z银行结合金融科技深化改革，初步完成了数字化转型，并在2020年提出“大财富”管理战略，助力Z银行向3.0模式转变。本文旨在围绕Z银行轻型银行转型变革之路，探究其改革动因、创新举措及学习相关经验，为同业银行提供重要参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the context of China&#39;s 14th Five-Year Plan policy environment and the Internet, the banking industry pays more attention to high-quality development, and the asset-light operation mode with digital as the carrier has become the strategic first choice of banks.As early as 2004, Z Bank took the initiative to take the road of &quot;light bank&quot; reform, committed to transform into the best commercial bank in China, adhere to the strategic goal of light bank, with retail business as the core, realize the transformation from 1.0 mode to 2.0 mode; with the continuous development of The Times, the digital migration of service channels and carriers, digital customer transaction behavior, trade and cross-border competition.In the face of environmental changes, Z Bank deepened the reform combined with fintech, initially completed the digital transformation, and put forward the &quot;big wealth&quot; management strategy in 2020 to help Z Bank transform to the 3.0 model.This paper aims to explore its reform motivation, innovative measures and learning related experience around the road of Z Bank light bank transformation and reform, so as to provide an important reference for interbank banks.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">业务层战略；轻型银行转型战略；战略构型理论；RBV理论；大财富管理；MAU；AUM；平台化战略；差异化战略；价值链分析；企业战略转型的实现方式</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-06</td>
                            </tr>
